title: Bloomberg Markets 1/9/2026
description: "Bloomberg Markets" follows the market moves across every global asset class and discusses the biggest issues for Wall Street. Today's guests: Vanessa Neumann, a former Venezuelan opposition representative to the UK and founder of advisory firm Asymmetrica, Jennifer Hillmant, Former Vice Chair of the US Internal Trade Commission and a former Member of the World Trade Organization Appellate Body (Source: Bloomberg)
